en:
[Current Team]: Exports a paste for the current team and copies them to clipboard if applicable.
[Tape Storage]: Exports the paste from storage. Always saves the text file externally.

[Plain Text]: Plain text format.
[Markdown]: Plain text inside a code block, used for Markdown or Discord.
[BBCode]: BBCode with colour formatting.
[HTML]: Always exports as an HTML file with colour formatting.
Suppresses tape nicknames when exporting paste.
Treats the tape as being 5 stars and suppresses grade when exporting paste.
Includes attributes in the exported paste.
Skips empty slots in the exported paste.

[Plain Text]: Plain text format.
[Markdown]: Plain text inside a code block, used for Markdown or Discord.
[BBCode]: BBCode with colour formatting.
[HTML Snippet]: HTML snippet with colour formatting.
[HTML Standalone]: Always exports as an HTML file.
